Create a modern Communication Management module for a MERN stack Education ERP / Academy Management System called “Pro Stack Academy”.

The feature should focus ONLY on WhatsApp Web integration using `whatsapp-web.js`.

Purpose:
Allow institute admins to send WhatsApp messages, payment receipts, reminders, attendance alerts, and PDFs directly to students using the institute’s own WhatsApp account connected through QR code scanning.

Theme:

* Modern UI
* Clean SaaS dashboard
* Orange + Black + White theme
* Responsive design
* Professional enterprise feel
* Use Tailwind CSS
* Use React.js frontend
* Node.js + Express backend
* MongoDB database

Tech Stack:
Frontend:

* React.js
* Tailwind CSS
* Redux Toolkit
* Axios

Backend:

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB
* Socket.IO
* whatsapp-web.js

Main Feature Requirements:

1. WhatsApp Web Connection

* Integrate `whatsapp-web.js`
* Generate QR code dynamically
* QR should auto-refresh automatically
* Admin scans QR using WhatsApp mobile app
* Show connection status:

  * Connected
  * Connecting
  * Disconnected
* Store WhatsApp session locally
* Auto reconnect after server restart
* Add Disconnect button
* Add Last Connected Time
* Add Connected Phone Number display
* Show QR refresh countdown timer
* Display “QR refreshes in 45 seconds”

2. Sidebar Navigation
   Add a new dedicated sidebar section for communication.

Sidebar Structure:

Dashboard
Students
Enquiry
Batch Management
Courses
Payments
Attendance
Examinations
Placement Drives
Reports

NEW SECTION:
Communication

* WhatsApp Web
* Email Templates
* SMS Templates
* Message Logs

Settings

Sidebar Requirements:

* Modern WhatsApp icon
* Active menu highlight
* Smooth hover animations
* Collapse/expand sidebar animation
* Responsive mobile drawer
* Dark sidebar theme
* Notification badge support
* Failed message count indicator
* Unread message indicator

Role-Based Visibility:

* Super Admin → Full Access
* Admin → Communication Access
* Students → No Access

3. Dedicated WhatsApp Communication Dashboard
   Create a full-page Communication Dashboard UI.

Layout Sections:

* WhatsApp Connection Status Card
* QR Scan Card
* Send Message Section
* Bulk Message Section
* Recent Activity Logs
* Delivery Analytics
* Message Statistics
* Quick Actions Panel
* Tips/Instructions Card

Design Requirements:

* Premium SaaS dashboard UI
* Glassmorphism effects
* Rounded cards
* Soft shadows
* Modern animations
* Responsive grid system
* Mobile optimized
* Enterprise CRM style UI
* Similar quality to Stripe, Notion, Linear dashboards

4. QR Connection Flow UI
   Show clear onboarding instructions:

Step 1:
Open WhatsApp on your phone

Step 2:
Go to Linked Devices

Step 3:
Tap Link a Device

Step 4:
Scan QR Code

Display:

* Large QR code
* Connection progress
* Refresh indicator
* Real-time connection updates using Socket.IO

5. Send Message Feature
   Admin should be able to:

* Send single message
* Send bulk messages
* Select students
* Select entire batch
* Select course
* Search students dynamically
* Type custom message
* Preview message
* Add emojis
* Attach files

Supported Attachments:

* PDF
* DOC
* DOCX
* Images

Add:

* Send button
* Preview button
* Character counter
* Upload progress

6. Student Integration
   Students collection contains:

* name
* phone
* email
* course
* batch
* payment details
* attendance details

Admin can directly send:

* payment receipts
* fee reminders
* attendance alerts
* class reminders
* welcome messages
* exam notifications
* placement updates

7. Payment Receipt Automation
   When payment is completed:

* Automatically generate PDF receipt
* Send receipt through WhatsApp automatically

Receipt should contain:

* Academy logo
* Student name
* Course name
* Amount paid
* Pending amount
* Invoice number
* Payment date
* Payment method
* Academy contact details

8. WhatsApp Activity Logs
   Create message history table showing:

* student name
* phone number
* message type
* attachment info
* delivery status
* sent time
* provider
* admin sender name

Statuses:

* Sent
* Delivered
* Read
* Failed

Add:

* filters
* search
* pagination
* export logs feature

9. Real-Time Updates
   Use Socket.IO for:

* QR code updates
* connection status
* live message delivery updates
* reconnect events
* real-time notifications

