12. Security Features

* JWT authentication
* Role-based permissions
* Admin-only messaging access
* Session encryption
* Rate limiting
* API validation
* Secure file uploads

13. Admin Experience
    Admin should NOT configure technical APIs manually.

The workflow should be:

Open Communication Page
→ Scan QR Code
→ Connected Successfully
→ Start Sending Messages

Keep UX extremely simple for non-technical institute admins.

